name.k: Max: HBO, TV, Sports et films

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Whether youre looking for the latest cant-miss dramas, comedies, or reality hits, Max has something for everyone. Watch HBO Original series like Succession, The Last of Us, The White Lotus, and Love & Death. Revisit classics like Friends, South Park, and The Big Bang Theory. And enjoy unscripted treats from Discovery like Fixer Upper, MythBusters, Dr. Pimple Popper, Deadliest Catch, and Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives.
Whether it's watching HBO Original series like Succession  revisiting classics like Friends  or enjoying treats from Discovery like Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives  Max has something for everyone.
Entre les sries originales de HBO comme Succession, les classiques comme Friends ou les petits plaisirs de Discovery comme Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Max a de quoi ravir tout le monde.
